tc.)\n\n## Relevant Files\n- `src/index.css` — Design system (variables, globals, typography)\n- `src/App.css` — Main layout container, responsiveness\n- `src/components/ScoreBoard.css` — Grid layout, centering fix\n- `src/components/PointButtons.css` — Touch targets, responsive buttons\n- `src/components/TeamScore.css` — Dominant score visual, responsive sizing\n- `src/components/GameStatus.css` — Malas/Buenas feedback, animation\n- `src/components/ResetButton.css` — Haptic feedback, responsive\n- `openspec/changes/archive/2026-05-06-team-score-component/` — Completed change",
