te_productos.sql, 003_create_product_categories.sql, 004_create_product_ingredients.sql)\n- ✅ Created migration runner script (config/migrations_productos.py)\n- ✅ Marked tasks 1.1-5.4 complete in tasks.md (13/55 tasks, 31% of work)\n- ✅ Created git commit: \"feat(product): implement product CRUD with stock calculation and integrity validation\"\n- 🔴 Identified Change 7 needed: refactor-categoria-ingrediente to add Service Layer to Categorías + Ingredientes modules\n\n## Next Steps\n- Create Change 7 (refactor-categoria-ingrediente) as a dedicated refactoring task\n- Continue Change 6 with Tasks 6-13 (backend tests, frontend, E2E)\n- Archive both changes when complete\n\n## Relevant Files\n- models/producto.py — Product + ProductIngredient domain models\n- repositories/producto_repository.py — ProductRepository + ProductIngredientRepository\n- backend/services/product_service.py — ProductService (business logic + validation)\n- backend/schemas/product_schema.py — 7 Pydantic schemas\n- backend/routers/productos.py — 6 REST endpoints\n- backend/routers/categorias.py — DELETE endpoint modified (line ~220-270)\n- backend/routers/ingredientes.py — DELETE endpoint modified (line ~280-330)\n- uow/interfaces.py, uow/inmemory.py — UoW with productos repositories\n- docs/migrations/002_*.sql, 003_*.sql, 004_*.sql — Product tables\n- config/migrations_productos.py — Migration runner\n- openspec/changes/producto-crud/tasks.md — 13 complete, 42 pending",
