      "content": "## Goal\nComplete the OPSX proposal-design-specs-tasks phase for the `carrito-pedidos` change: design the carrito client-side (Zustand + localStorage) and atomic order creation (backend transactional with UoW, price/direction snapshots, stock validation).\n\n## Instructions\n- Project: `repositoriobasefoodstore-sdd` (use this exact name for memory consistency)\n- Change map is in `docs/CHANGES.md` (save if lost)\n- OPSX workflow: explore → propose → apply → archive (fluid, no phase locks)\n- Next change after carrito-pedidos: pago-gestion (depends on pedidos complete)\n- Always check `openspec list --json` and `openspec status --change \"name\" --json` for state\n\n## Discoveries\n- OPSX status parsing: `applyRequires` field tells you what's needed before apply phase\n- CartStore (Zustand) MUST use localStorage plugin for persistence (RN-CR02: cart survives page refresh + logout/login)\n- Snapshots are IMMUTABLE: precio_snapshot and direccion_snapshot stored at order creation time, changes to products/directions don't affect existing orders (RN-PE02, RN-PE03, RN-DA06)\n- Stock validation MUST use SELECT FOR UPDATE inside transaction to prevent race conditions (RN-PE04)\n- HistorialEstadoPedido is append-only: NEVER UPDATE/DELETE, only INSERT (RN-DA05, RN-FS07)\n- PersonalizacionDTO: array of excluded ingrediente_ids, stored as INTEGER[] or JSON in detalle_pedido (RN-CR05, RN-PE07)\n- PedidoService transactional flow: begin → validate stock → generate snapshots → INSERT pedido + detalles + historial → commit/rollback (atomic)\n\n## Accomplished\n- ✅ Created `carrito-pedidos` change via `openspec new change \"carrito-pedidos\"`\n- ✅ Wrote `proposal.md`: Why (e-commerce core), What Changes (backend API + frontend stores/components), Capabilities (7 new), Impact (models, tables, endpoints)\n- ✅ Wrote `design.md`: Full architecture diagram (frontend → HTTP → backend → DB), PedidoService pseudocode with transactional guarantees, component details, validation rules, error handling (RFC 7807)\n- ✅ Created 3 delta specs in `specs/`:\n  - `carrito-frontend.md`: CartStore (Zustand) with capabilities (init, add, remove, update qty, get total, serialize)\n  - `pedido-creacion.md`: Backend atomic order creation with stock validation, snapshots, 3 new tables (pedidos, detalles_pedido, historial_estado_pedido), Pydantic schemas, transactional guarantees\n  - `checkout-ui.md`: React components (CartItemList, CartSummary, DirectionSelector, CreateOrderButton, OrderConfirmationModal) with data flow and error handling\n- ✅ Created `tasks.md`: 83 tasks across 13 sections (1.Database, 2.Repositories, 3.ServiceLayer, 4.Endpoints, 5.BackendTests, 6.CartStore, 7.Components, 8.CheckoutPage, 9.HTTPClient, 10.FrontendTests, 11.Integration, 12.Docs, 13.Verification)\n- ✅ Verified change completeness: `openspec status --change \"carrito-pedidos\" --json` shows all artifacts \"done\"\n- ✅ Committed to git: `feat(carrito-pedidos): proposal, design, specs, tasks complete`\n\n## Next Steps\n- 🔄 **Apply phase** (when ready): `openspec apply carrito-pedidos`\n  - Priority: Backend first (Alembic migrations → models → repos → service → endpoints → tests)\n  - Then: Frontend (CartStore → Components → CheckoutPage → tests)\n  - Keep this pattern: spec → implement → test → move to next\n- 📋 **After carrito-pedidos**: `pago-gestion` (payment integration with MercadoPago)\n- 📊 **Archive workflow**: When all 83 tasks complete → `openspec archive carrito-pedidos --yes`\n\n## Relevant Files\n- `openspec/changes/carrito-pedidos/proposal.md` — Business case and scope\n- `openspec/changes/carrito-pedidos/design.md` — Technical architecture and service layer pseudocode\n- `openspec/changes/carrito-pedidos/specs/carrito-frontend.md` — CartStore spec (Zustand + localStorage)\n- `openspec/changes/carrito-pedidos/specs/pedido-creacion.md` — Backend order creation spec (transactional, snapshots)\n- `openspec/changes/carrito-pedidos/specs/checkout-ui.md` — Frontend components spec\n- `openspec/changes/carrito-pedidos/tasks.md` — 83-task implementation checklist\n- `docs/CHANGES.md` — Master change map for entire project (8 complete, 6 pending after carrito-pedidos)",
