      "content": "## Goal\nImplement sprint-1-auth change: full auth module backend + frontend (80/88 tasks complete, 8 left = manual validation 19.x)\n\n## Instructions\n- Project uses OPSX/OpenSpec workflow — all changes tracked under openspec/changes/sprint-1-auth/\n- CLAUDE.md rules are strict: no session.commit() in services, Feature-Sliced Design, no `any` in TS\n- UoW pattern: Router uses `with UnitOfWork() as uow:` context manager, security.py `get_current_user` uses `Depends(get_uow)` generator\n\n## Discoveries\n- auth/model.py had `id: int PK + token_hash` (wrong), migrated to `jti: UUID PK` — needed manual migration file 002_refresh_tokens_jti.py\n- UoW already had all repository imports hardcoded → needed to create stub repositories for ALL 7 modules (roles, categorias, ingredientes, productos, direcciones, pedidos, pagos) or the app would fail to start\n- Slowapi limiter was in main.py → moved to core/limiter.py to avoid circular import with auth/router.py\n- security.py get_uow uses LOCAL import of UnitOfWork inside the function body to avoid circular imports at module load time\n- authStore was missing refreshToken field — interceptor couldn't send refresh_token in body (design flaw from sprint-0 scaffold)\n- TanStack Form v0.24.x API: useForm() + form.Field + field.state.value/meta.errors\n- uiStore didn't have toast support — added addToast/removeToast + ToastItem[] array\n\n## Accomplished\n- ✅ auth/model.py — jti UUID PK, refresh_tokens table\n- ✅ core/security.py — create_access_token(sub,rol), create_refresh_token(sub)-\u003etuple, decode_token(token, expected_type), get_current_user-\u003eUsuario, require_role factory\n- ✅ core/limiter.py — shared limiter instance (new file)\n- ✅ core/uow.py — added get_uow() generator at bottom\n- ✅ usuarios/repository.py, auth/repository.py — created\n- ✅ roles/categorias/ingredientes/productos/direcciones/pedidos/pagos repository stubs — created\n- ✅ auth/schemas.py — 7 schemas (Register/Login/TokenResponse/Refresh/Logout/UserPublic/ErrorResponse)\n- ✅ auth/service.py — register, login, refresh (anti-replay), logout, get_me\n- ✅ auth/router.py — 5 endpoints with limiter on /login\n- ✅ main.py — custom rate limit RFC7807 handler, uses core/limiter\n- ✅ alembic/versions/002_refresh_tokens_jti.py — manual migration\n- ✅ Frontend: types/auth.ts, api/endpoints/auth.ts, store/authStore.ts (rewrite with refreshToken), store/uiStore.ts (+ toasts)\n- ✅ Frontend: api/client.ts — checks code:ACCESS_TOKEN_EXPIRED, sends refresh_token in body\n- ✅ Frontend: hooks (useLogin, useRegister, useLogout, useCurrentUser)\n- ✅ Frontend: components (LoginForm, RegisterForm, ProtectedRoute)\n- ✅ Frontend: layouts (AppLayout, AdminLayout, Navbar, Sidebar)\n- ✅ Frontend: App.tsx with full routing (public/protected/admin)\n- ✅ Frontend: pages (LoginPage, RegisterPage updated)\n- ✅ Tests: conftest.py + 6 backend test files + 4 frontend test files (authStore, ProtectedRoute, LoginForm, RegisterForm)\n- ✅ package.json — added vitest + testing-library + msw, test script\n- ✅ tasks.md — 80/88 marked complete\n- 🔲 19.x: Manual validation (pytest, npm test, uvicorn, npm run dev, end-to-end flows) — requires running PostgreSQL\n\n## Relevant Files\n- backend/app/modules/auth/model.py — RefreshToken with jti UUID PK\n- backend/app/modules/auth/repository.py — create_token/get_by_jti/revoke/revoke_all_by_user\n- backend/app/modules/auth/schemas.py — all auth schemas\n- backend/app/modules/auth/service.py — register/login/refresh/logout/get_me\n- backend/app/modules/auth/router.py — 5 FastAPI endpoints\n- backend/app/core/security.py — hash/verify/create_access_token/create_refresh_token/decode_token/get_current_user/require_role\n- backend/app/core/limiter.py — shared slowapi Limiter instance (new)\n- backend/app/core/uow.py — added get_uow() generator\n- backend/alembic/versions/002_refresh_tokens_jti.py — migration\n- frontend/src/store/authStore.ts — rewritten with TokenResponse/UserPublic types + refreshToken\n- frontend/src/store/uiStore.ts — added toast state\n- frontend/src/api/client.ts — full interceptor with refresh + toast\n- frontend/src/App.tsx — full routing with layouts and ProtectedRoute",
