      "content": "**What**: Implemented sprint-8-admin-metricas — full admin panel with metrics, user management, stock table, and configuration panel. All 63 tasks complete.\n\n**Why**: Sprint 8 completing the Food Store admin panel. Previously had auth, catalog, cart, checkout, payments, orders FSM, and partial admin (categorias/ingredientes). Missing: user RBAC management, business metrics dashboard, stock management with include_deleted, configuration UI.\n\n**Where**:\n- backend/app/modules/admin/schemas.py — Pydantic schemas for all admin responses\n- backend/app/modules/admin/repository.py — AdminRepository with user queries + metrics queries (SQLite strftime, not date_trunc)\n- backend/app/modules/admin/service.py — AdminService stateless, validates RN-RB03/RN-RB04\n- backend/app/modules/admin/router.py — 8 endpoints under /api/v1/admin/\n- backend/app/core/uow.py — added uow.admin = AdminRepository\n- backend/app/modules/productos/router.py — added include_deleted query param (honors only for ADMIN via JWT decode)\n- backend/app/modules/productos/service.py — passes include_deleted down\n- backend/app/modules/productos/repository.py — conditions deleted_at filter based on include_deleted\n- frontend/src/types/admin.ts — all admin TypeScript interfaces\n- frontend/src/api/endpoints/admin.ts — 8 API functions\n- frontend/src/features/admin/hooks/ — 6 new hooks (metricas, ventas, top productos, pedidos estado, usuarios, mutations)\n- frontend/src/features/admin/components/ — 9 new components (KpiCard, VentasLineChart, ProductosTopBarChart, PedidosPieChart, Dashboard, UsuariosTable, EditarRolesModal, UsuariosCRUD, StockTable, ConfiguracionPanel)\n- frontend/src/App.tsx — added routes /admin, /admin/usuarios, /admin/stock, /admin/configuracion\n- frontend/src/components/layouts/Sidebar.tsx — added Stock and Configuración items\n\n**Learned**:\n- Dev DB is SQLite (foodstore_dev.db), so metrics queries use func.strftime() NOT date_trunc(). Would need to swap for P