      "content": "## Goal\nComplete implementation of C-04 (rbac-permisos-finos) — fine-grained RBAC for the activia-trace backend.\n\n## Instructions\n- No DB mocks — all tests use real PostgreSQL (trace_test_db)\n- Identity always from JWT session (never URL/body/header params)\n- Multi-tenancy row-level: every repo filters by tenant_id by default\n- Fail-closed: 403 (not 401) when permission missing; 401 reserved for unauthenticated\n- AlcanceEnum: `global_` in Python (keyword clash), stored as \"global\" in PG via values_callable\n- Tests making HTTP requests MUST commit (not just flush) before the request — handler uses a separate session\n\n## Discoveries\n- Coverage tool needs dotted module names (`app.services.rbac_service`), not path separators\n- FastAPI 204 responses need `response_model=None` explicitly or test fails with \"must not have body\"\n- `create_app()` fails at import due to C-03 Pydantic forward ref bug on `LoginRequest` — admin tests use a minimal FastAPI app with only the rbac router as workaround\n- Pre-existing failures (test_app_startup × 4, test_get_totp_uri × 1) existed before C-04; not caused by this change\n- AlcanceEnum stores \"global\"/\"propio\" via `values_callable=lambda obj: [e.value for e in obj]` not \"global_\"\n- GATE 4 in CHANGES.md is now unlocked: C-04 complete → C-05, C-06, C-21 can start in parallel\n\n## Accomplished\n- ✅ 4 new SQLAlchemy models: Rol, Permiso, RolPermiso (with AlcanceEnum PG native enum), UsuarioRol\n- ✅ Alembic migration 004 + idempotent seed (7 roles, 22 perms, full matrix from KB §3.3)\n- ✅ 4 RBAC repositories extending BaseRepository with mandatory tenant scope\n- ✅ RbacService.resolver_permisos_efectivos — JOIN chain, vigencia filter, global wins over propio (100% coverage)\n- ✅ require_permission factory in app/core/permissions.py — fail-closed, PermisoConcedido dataclass\n- ✅ Pydantic v2 schemas (extra='forbid') + RbacAdminService + /api/rbac router\n- ✅ 35 tests green: 10 seed + 5 repo + 8 service + 7 guard + 5 admin\n- ✅ All 26 tasks marked [x] in tasks.md\n- ✅ Full test suite: 127 passed (pre-existing 3 failures not caused by C-04)\n\n## Relevant Files\n- `backend/app/models/rol.py` — new Rol model\n- `backend/app/models/permiso.py` — new Permiso model\n- `backend/app/models/rol_permiso.py` — new RolPermiso + AlcanceEnum\n- `backend/app/models/usuario_rol.py` — new UsuarioRol with vigencia\n- `backend/app/models/__init__.py` — all 6 models registered\n- `backend/alembic/versions/004_rbac_catalog.py` — migration + seed call\n- `backend/app/services/rbac_seed.py` — idempotent seed, 7 roles, 22 perms\n- `backend/app/services/rbac_service.py` — permission resolver, 100% coverage\n- `backend/app/core/permissions.py` — require_permission factory, PermisoConcedido\n- `backend/app/services/rbac_admin_service.py` — CRUD service for RBAC catalog\n- `backend/app/api/v1/routers/rbac.py` — admin router at /api/rbac\n- `backend/tests/test_rbac_*.py` — 35 tests across 5 files\n- `openspec/changes/c-04-rbac-permisos-finos/tasks.md` — all 26/26 tasks done",
