      "content": "**What**: Implemented all 50 tasks for C-07 — `Usuario` and `Asignacion` models with full CRUD stack.\n\n**Why**: Next link in the critical path after C-06 (academic catalog). Required to unblock C-08 (alumnos), C-09 (equipos), and all domain modules.\n\n**Where**:\n- `backend/app/models/usuario.py` — Usuario model, __tablename__=\"usuarios\", PII as ciphertext\n- `backend/app/models/asignacion.py` — Asignacion model, __tablename__=\"asignaciones\"\n- `backend/app/core/crypto.py` — added `hash_deterministic(value) -\u003e str` (HMAC-SHA256)\n- `backend/alembic/versions/007_usuarios_y_asignaciones.py` — revision=007, down_revision=006\n- `backend/app/repositories/usuario_repository.py` — get_by_email_hash(), list_activos()\n- `backend/app/repositories/asignacion_repository.py` — list_with_filters() with 6 optional params\n- `backend/app/schemas/usuario.py` — UsuarioCreate/Update/Response (email_hash absent from response)\n- `backend/app/schemas/asignacion.py` — RolNegocioEnum, AsignacionCreate/Update/Response with estado_vigencia\n- `backend/app/services/usuario_service.py` — encrypt on write, decrypt on read via UsuarioDecifrado DTO\n- `backend/app/services/asignacion_service.py` — computes estado_vigencia at read time\n- `backend/app/api/v1/routers/usuarios.py` — /api/admin/usuarios, guard usuarios:gestionar\n- `backend/app/api/v1/routers/asignaciones.py` — /api/asignaciones, guard equipos:asignar on writes\n- `backend/app/models/__init__.py` — added Usuario, Asignacion exports\n- `backend/app/main.py` — registered both routers\n- `backend/tests/test_usuarios_modelos.py`, `test_usuarios_services.py`, `test_usuarios_endpoints.py` — 31 tests total\n\n**Learned**:\n- PII encrypt/decrypt lives ONLY in UsuarioService (not model, not router)\n- email_hash = HMAC-SHA256(key=AES_KEY, msg=email.strip().lower()) for deterministic uniqueness index\n- estado_vigencia is NEVER persisted — computed at read time: Vigente if desde\u003c=today AND (hasta IS NULL OR today\u003c=hasta)\n- Asignacion.rol is a business string enum, NOT a FK to RBAC roles table (D-05)\n- Migration seeds 3 permissions (usuarios:gestionar, equipos:asignar, asignaciones:gestionar) defensively with ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING",
