      "title": "C-20 perfil-y-mensajeria-interna implemented",
      "content": "**What**: Implemented C-20 (perfil-y-mensajeria-interna) — all 34 tasks complete.\n\n**Why**: Closes Épica 11 (self-service profile) and F3.4 (internal messaging). Users can now manage their own profile without ADMIN intervention; registered users can exchange internal messages in threads.\n\n**Where**:\n- `backend/app/models/usuario.py` — added sexo (String50 nullable) and modalidad_cobro (String20 nullable) columns\n- `backend/app/models/mensaje.py` — NEW: Mensaje entity (thread_id, remitente_id, destinatario_id, asunto, cuerpo, leido_at)\n- `backend/app/models/__init__.py` — registered Mensaje\n- `backend/alembic/versions/017_perfil_y_mensajeria.py` — NEW: migration (ADD COL usuarios + CREATE TABLE mensajes)\n- `backend/app/services/usuario_service.py` — extended UsuarioDecifrado, create, update with sexo/modalidad_cobro\n- `backend/app/services/perfil_service.py` — NEW: PerfilService (resolves user_id from JWT, delegates to UsuarioService)\n- `backend/app/services/mensaje_service.py` — NEW: MensajeService (enviar, listar_inbox, leer_hilo, responder)\n- `backend/app/repositories/mensaje_repository.py` — NEW: MensajeRepository (list_inbox, get_thread, is_participant, mark_thread_read, get_other_participant, get_thread_subject)\n- `backend/app/schemas/perfil.py` — NEW: PerfilResponse (no email_hash), PerfilUpdate (no cuil — extra=forbid)\n- `backend/app/schemas/mensaje.py` — NEW: MensajeCreate, MensajeResponse, ThreadResponse, RespuestaCreate, ThreadSummaryResponse\n- `backend/app/schemas/usuario.py` — added sexo, modalidad_cobro to UsuarioCreate, UsuarioUpdate, UsuarioResponse\n- `backend/app/api/v1/routers/perfil.py` — NEW: GET /api/perfil, PATCH /api/perfil\n- `backend/app/api/v1/routers/inbox.py` — NEW: POST /api/inbox, GET /api/inbox, GET /api/inbox/{thread_id}, POST /api/inbox/{thread_id}/responder\n- `backend/app/main.py` — registered perfil and inbox routers\n- `backend/tests/test_perfil.py` — NEW: 7 tests (schema validation, service, endpoint integration)\n- `backend/tests/test_mensajeria.py` — NEW: 13 tests (repository, service, endpoint integration)\n\n**Learned**:\n- The token function in the project is `create_access_token(user_id, tenant_id, roles, secret_key, expire_minutes)` — NOT `create_token`. Check security.py before writing test helpers.\n- The FastAPI version installed has a pre-existing `Router.__init__() got unexpected kwarg 'on_startup'` error — this is unrelated to C-20 and affects all routers; the app can't be imported at module level but tests still run.\n- The `from_attributes=True` in Pydantic _Base allows `model_validate()` to work with Python @dataclass DTOs (UsuarioDecifrado, MensajeDTO) — Pydantic uses getattr which works on dataclasses.\n- CUIL immutability is implemented declaratively via schema (PerfilUpdate has no cuil field + extra=forbid) — cleaner than conditional logic.\n- `MensajeService` stores `_tenant_id` directly rather than accessing `self._repo._tenant_id` (protected attr access antipattern).",
