      "title": "OPSX apply completed: C-21 frontend-shell-y-auth",
      "content": "**What**: Implemented all 39 tasks for C-21 — complete React 18 SPA scaffolded in `frontend/` from scratch.\n\n**Why**: Backend auth (C-03) and RBAC (C-04) were complete. C-21 creates the frontend foundation needed for C-22/C-23/C-24.\n\n**Where**:\n- `frontend/` — entire new directory (React 18 + TS + Vite + Tailwind v4 + TanStack Query + RHF/Zod + Axios + React Router)\n- `frontend/src/shared/services/tokenStorage.ts` — localStorage abstraction for access/refresh tokens\n- `frontend/src/shared/services/jwtDecode.ts` — typed JWT payload decoder (no sig verification)\n- `frontend/src/shared/services/api.ts` — Axios instance with 401→refresh→retry interceptor (isRefreshing flag + pendingRequests queue), 403 propagated as AccessDeniedError, `setAuthCallbacks` for non-React clearSession\n- `frontend/src/features/auth/context/AuthContext.tsx` — Context + useReducer, synchronous init via lazy initializer (avoids auth flash)\n- `frontend/src/features/auth/hooks/` — useLogin, useVerify2fa, useForgotPassword, useResetPassword, useLogout\n- `frontend/src/features/auth/pages/` — LoginPage, TwoFactorPage, ForgotPasswordPage, ResetPasswordPage\n- `frontend/src/shared/components/` — RequireAuth, RequireRole, AppShell, NavMenu, AccessDeniedPage\n- `frontend/src/router/index.tsx` — public auth routes + private shell routes\n- `frontend/src/test/` + 4 test files (AuthContext, api, guards, AppShell) — 20 tests, all passing\n- `openspec/changes/c-21-frontend-shell-y-auth/tasks.md` — 39/39 tasks marked [x]\n\n**Learned**:\n- Tailwind v4 uses `@tailwindcss/vite` plugin (no tailwind.config.js), `@import \"tailwindcss\"` in CSS\n- TS6 `erasableSyntaxOnly` mode disallows class declarations in some configs → error classes written as factory functions\n- AuthContext uses lazy initializer pattern in useReducer to hydrate synchronously from localStorage (avoids unauthenticated flash before guards run)\n- `setAuthCallbacks` pattern needed to let api.ts (non-React module) call clearSession on refresh failure\n- TwoFactorPage reads partial_token from React Router location.state; ResetPasswordPage reads token from URL search params\n- MSW v2 uses `http` + `HttpResponse` API (not `rest` from v1)\n- Nav menu items: Dashboard=all roles, Gestión=ADMIN+COORDINADOR, Alumnos=TUTOR+PROFESOR+COORDINADOR+ADMIN+NEXO, Finanzas=FINANZAS+ADMIN\n- Production build: 465 kB JS, 14 kB CSS, zero TS errors",
