      "content": "**What**: Scaffolded the Iuris React frontend and implemented all 13 screens from the Iuris.dc.html design prototype.\n\n**Why**: User requested \"Implement: Iuris.dc.html\" — convert the HTML design prototype (project b438cdf9-bff8-4a05-833d-82338e51c895 on claude.ai/design) to a real React app.\n\n**Where**:\n- frontend/package.json — React 18 + react-router-dom v6 + pdf-lib + TypeScript + Vite\n- frontend/vite.config.ts — Vite with proxy to backend :8000\n- frontend/index.html — Google Fonts (Inter + Playfair Display)\n- frontend/src/index.css — reset + animations (fadeIn/mIn) + scrollbar\n- frontend/src/main.tsx — entry point\n- frontend/src/shared/http.ts — fetch client with HttpOnly cookie auth + CSRF header\n- frontend/src/shared/types.ts — shared domain types (Usuario, Cliente, Caso, Etapa, etc.)\n- frontend/src/app/AuthContext.tsx — auth context with mock SOCIO user\n- frontend/src/app/App.tsx — lazy-loaded routes with RequireAuth + RequireSocio guards\n- frontend/src/app/AppShell.tsx — sidebar (240px, #0C1E3E) + topbar (58px, white) + content area\n\n**Learned**:\n- Design uses inline styles throughout — React implementation follows same approach for faithful conversion\n- All colors/typography from design: primary #1B3A6B, gold #C9A028, sidebar #0C1E3E, content bg #F2F0EA\n- Font families: Inter (body) + Playfair Display (headings/logo)\n- Feature-first architecture: features/ (13 screens) + shared/ + app/\n- Existing telegramas feature files were preserved (types.ts, api.ts, hooks/, utils/)\n- isSocio flag gates Usuarios + Respaldos routes\n- Routes: /login (no shell), / routes nested under AppShell (Outlet pattern)\n- Screens: login, dashboard, casos, nuevo-caso, caso-laboral, caso-art, clientes, nuevo-cliente, actualizaciones (batch), telegrama, agenda, usuarios, respaldos",
