r + content Outlet\n- ✅ frontend/src/features/auth/LoginPage.tsx — gradient bg, animated card, email/password\n- ✅ frontend/src/features/dashboard/DashboardPage.tsx — 4 metric cards + pending updates table + vencimientos list\n- ✅ frontend/src/features/casos/CasosPage.tsx — table with filters, area tabs, search\n- ✅ frontend/src/features/casos/NuevoCasoPage.tsx — 2-col form: client search + area radio + abogado + resumen sidebar\n- ✅ frontend/src/features/casos/CasoLaboralPage.tsx — 10-step stepper, documents, historial, IAModal, confirm-retroceder modal\n- ✅ frontend/src/features/casos/CasoARTPage.tsx — 8-step stepper, teal theme, no telegrama button\n- ✅ frontend/src/features/comunicaciones/IAModal.tsx — named export, backdrop blur, editable draft, AI notice banner\n- ✅ frontend/src/features/comunicaciones/BatchPage.tsx — split panel: item list + draft editor + AI notice + approve/discard\n- ✅ frontend/src/features/clientes/ClientesPage.tsx — table with live search filter\n- ✅ frontend/src/features/clientes/NuevoClientePage.tsx — 4-section admission form + sticky save sidebar\n- ✅ frontend/src/features/telegramas/TelegramaPage.tsx — 3-section form + live monospace preview (Courier New)\n- ✅ frontend/src/features/agenda/AgendaPage.tsx — June 2026 calendar grid + event pills + upcoming movements panel\n- ✅ frontend/src/features/usuarios/UsuariosPage.tsx — user table + create user form (SOCIO only)\n- ✅ frontend/src/features/respaldos/RespaldosPage.tsx — backup table + status banner (SOCIO only)\n- ✅ frontend/favicon.svg\n\n## Relevant Files\n- frontend/src/app/App.tsx — router; all routes defined here\n- frontend/src/app/AppShell.tsx — sidebar + topbar; all nav items\n- frontend/src/app/AuthContext.tsx — auth state; mock SOCIO user hardcoded here\n- frontend/src/shared/http.ts — HTTP client; change base URL here if backend URL changes\n- frontend/src/features/telegramas/TelegramaPage.tsx — NEW styled page (GeneradorTelegrama.tsx in components/ still exists but is not rendered directly)",
