      "content": "**What**: Implemented all 30 tasks for change `migraciones-esquema-base`. Full SQLAlchemy + Alembic schema for the Iuris platform.\n\n**Why**: RNF-09 in changemap — establish database schema base with migrations before feature implementation.\n\n**Where**:\n- `backend/requirements.txt` — added sqlalchemy==2.0.36, alembic==1.14.0, psycopg2-binary==2.9.10\n- `backend/app/shared/enums.py` — all 12 Postgres enums as Python enum classes + SA type objects\n- `backend/app/core/db_base.py` — DeclarativeBase with ix/uq/fk/pk/ck naming convention\n- `backend/app/core/database.py` — engine, SessionLocal, get_db()\n- `backend/app/core/models_registry.py` — imports all 8 features/*/models.py\n- `backend/app/features/{auth,clientes,casos,telegramas,documentos,vencimientos,comunicaciones,backups}/models.py` — 13 tables total\n- `backend/alembic/` + `backend/alembic.ini` — alembic setup\n- `backend/alembic/versions/001_esquema_base_inicial.py` — full upgrade/downgrade\n- `backend/entrypoint.sh` — runs alembic upgrade head before uvicorn\n- `backend/Dockerfile` — updated to use entrypoint.sh\n- `docs/changemap.md` — RNF-09 marked ✅ Implementado\n\n**Learned**:\n- Enums defined once in `shared/enums.py` with `create_type=False` in column defs to avoid duplicate metadata registration\n- Migration creates enums via `_create_enums()` with `checkfirst=True` before any tables\n- `depends_on: db: condition: service_healthy` was already in docker-compose — no change needed\n- Zero seed data in migration — etapas/transiciones belong to next change (ADR-0008)\n- All 8 feature dirs got `__init__.py` package markers\n- Next action: `/opsx:archive migraciones-esquema-base`",
